uecomment-501025779","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/16796","id":501025779,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUwMTAyNTc3OQ==","user":{"login":"sdlins","id":412490,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxMjQ5MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/412490?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins","html_url":"https://github.com/sdlins","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-06-11T21:15:15Z","updated_at":"2019-06-11T21:15:15Z","body":"I am tracing this again. \r\n\r\nTill now I found MSSQL has two functions: `sp_updateextendedproperty` and `sp_addextendedproperty`.\r\nI can test wether the description already exists before update or add a description. After `add` the description an `update` doesn't generate any errors.\r\n\r\nHope to make a PR next weeks, according to my free time.","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/comments/501025779/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"sdlins","id":412490,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxMjQ5MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/412490?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins","html_url":"https://github.com/sdlins","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/comments/501093970","html_url":"https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/issues/16796#issuecomment-501093970","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/yiisoft/yii2/issues/16796","id":501093970,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUwMTA5Mzk3MA==","user":{"login":"sdlins","id":412490,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxMjQ5MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/412490?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins","html_url":"https://github.com/sdlins","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sdlins/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-06-12T02:16:28Z","updated_at":"2019-06-12T16:25:46Z","body":"@samdark I would appreciate your help in a question.\r\n\r\nThis would be the new `mssql\\QueryBuilder::addCommentOnTable()` method:\r\n```php\r\n    public function addCommentOnTable($table, $comment)\r\n    {\r\n        $schemaName = $this->db->schema->defaultSchema;\r\n        $comment = $this->db->quoteValue($comment);\r\n\r\n        return <<< SQL\r\n        -- Maybe we can simplify this later\r\n        IF\r\n            NOT EXISTS (\r\n                SELECT 1\r\n                FROM fn_listextendedproperty (\r\n                    NULL,\r\n                    'SCHEMA', N'$schemaName',\r\n                    'TABLE', N'$table',\r\n                    null, null\r\n                )\r\n            )\r\n        BEGIN\r\n            EXEC sys.sp_addextendedproperty\r\n                @name = N'MS_description',\r\n                @value = $comment,\r\n                @level0type = N'SCHEMA', @level0name = N'$schemaName',\r\n                @level1type = N'TABLE', @level1name = N'$table';\r\n        END\r\n        ELSE\r\n        BEGIN\r\n            EXEC sys.sp_updateextendedproperty\r\n                @name = N'MS_description',\r\n                @value = $comment,\r\n                @level0type = N'SCHEMA', @level0name = N'$schemaName',\r\n                @level1type = N'TABLE', @level1name = N'$table';\r\n        END\r\n        GO\r\nSQL;\r\n    }\r\n```\r\nInstead of:\r\n\r\n```php\r\n    public function addCommentOnTable($table, $comment)\r\n    {\r\n        return \"sp_updateextendedproperty @name = N'MS_Description', @value = {$this->db->quoteValue($comment)}, @level1type = N'Table',  @level1name = {$this->db->quoteTableName($table)}\";\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn my tests, `sp_(whatever)extendedproperty()` will not work without schema name. But the `mssql\\Schema::defaultSchema` defaults to `null`. So, if schema name is not provided, this will generate an error. Should the docs be updated about it or do you see some other way? ","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":